Problem Statement:
 Prinnt the minimum positive integer divisible by both 2 and N .
 Input:3
 Output:6
 Expalanation:6 is divisible by both 2 and 3.Also,there is no  +ve integer less than 6 that is divisible by both 2 and 3.
 
 
 
 
 
 
 #########################################################################################################################################################################
 OUTPUT:
#include <iostream>
using namespace std;

int main() {
    int i=0,n;
    cin>>n;
while(true)
{
    i++;
    if((i%2==0) && (i%n==0))
    {
        cout<<i;
        break;
    }
}

    return 0;
}
